other_tests.findings: The liver demonstrates homogeneous low attenuation throughout with evidence of steatosis (29 to 38) on non-contrast scan. The pancreas shows interacinar fatty infiltration with no solid mass, and there is peripancreatic stranding and thickening of the left perirenal fascia compatible with inflammation. A small nonobstructing stone in the lower pole of the left kidney measures 7.7 mm.
